column5: Made it out for salmon a couple of times...  all pics in 1 report...  Port Weller Tourney Pre Fish  5 for 5      Port Weller Tourney  6 for 7  me praying to the fish gods... stomach was upset all day...    it worked, we were skunked up till that point...    4 fish box, ours weighed 40.1lbs, winning team 67 lbs  Bronte  7 for 9
Lake Ontarios finest !!!!!...great looking spring kings man,job well done !!!   i cant wait to get out there myself,maybe in a few weeks....cheers
Really nice fish there Goran but I don't see any of those snazzy rod holder systems on those boats. What's up with that?  Thanks for sharing.
nice fish Goran  Bronte has been very good lately. Will be out this weekend pm trips.
